WEBVTT

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:41.100 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.190 --> 00:01:43.730 line:80%
[Episode 14]

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:52.000 line:80%
Hurry, come!

00:01:52.870 --> 00:01:53.920 line:80%
Be careful.

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:57.110 line:80%
How beautiful!

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:58.640 line:80%
Isn't it?

00:01:58.640 --> 00:01:59.309 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:10.830 --> 00:02:11.830 line:80%
My dear,

00:02:16.670 --> 00:02:19.760 line:80%
thank you for staying with me
for another year.

00:02:22.670 --> 00:02:24.190 line:80%
You damn old man.

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:26.129 line:80%
You're still in the mood for this?

00:02:26.670 --> 00:02:30.129 line:80%
The older one gets, the more one should
possess a tender heart.

00:02:30.990 --> 00:02:33.110 line:80%
I guess this is why I chose you
as my life partner.

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:34.510 line:80%
Changning wants one too.

00:02:36.040 --> 00:02:37.670 line:80%
-You too?
-You want one too, Changning?

00:02:37.670 --> 00:02:38.879 line:80%
Changning, your hands are too small.

00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:39.990 line:80%
It won't stay on.

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:42.050 line:80%
Changning wants a partner too.

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:44.760 line:80%
You want a partner?

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.320 line:80%
Look, over there.

00:03:06.260 --> 00:03:07.170 line:80%
So,

00:03:08.700 --> 00:03:10.830 line:80%
this is how the New Year is celebrated.

00:03:11.540 --> 00:03:13.800 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:22.129 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.050 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:03:33.879 --> 00:03:35.040 line:80%
Happy...

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:37.950 line:80%
New Year.

00:03:42.270 --> 00:03:43.350 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:50.390 line:80%
If you don't enter the tiger's den,
you won't catch its cub.

00:03:57.320 --> 00:03:58.160 line:80%
What cub?

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:22.690 line:80%
Are you really drunk?

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:26.920 line:80%
Of course not.

00:04:30.190 --> 00:04:31.720 line:80%
I guess she's really drunk.

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:33.920 line:80%
Let's go. I'll take you back to your room.

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:35.110 line:80%
Don't move.

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:37.900 line:80%
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:37.120 line:80%
Don't move.

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:41.260 line:80%
♪ The most beautiful scenery becomes a poem ♪

00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:45.110 line:80%
♪ For a chance encounter  ♪

00:04:46.050 --> 00:04:49.600 line:80%
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

00:04:48.310 --> 00:04:50.140 line:80%
If I don't enter the tiger's den...

00:04:50.140 --> 00:04:52.280 line:80%
♪ I’ll burn out my passion for you ♪

00:04:52.750 --> 00:04:56.370 line:80%
♪ Just for a glance ♪

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.010 line:80%
I won't catch its cub.

00:04:56.740 --> 00:04:57.500 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:04:57.520 --> 00:04:59.910 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:04:59.930 --> 00:05:01.720 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:05:02.170 --> 00:05:03.020 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:05:03.050 --> 00:05:05.950 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:05:05.980 --> 00:05:07.910 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:05:07.940 --> 00:05:08.580 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:11.760 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:05:11.800 --> 00:05:13.910 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick  ♪

00:05:13.940 --> 00:05:18.620 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:05:19.170 --> 00:05:20.250 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:05:20.270 --> 00:05:22.990 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:05:23.010 --> 00:05:24.870 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:05:24.890 --> 00:05:25.890 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:05:25.910 --> 00:05:28.800 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:05:28.820 --> 00:05:30.780 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:05:30.820 --> 00:05:31.510 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:34.520 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:05:34.550 --> 00:05:36.720 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick  ♪

00:05:36.750 --> 00:05:41.760 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:05:41.780 --> 00:05:47.030 line:80%
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:46.990 line:80%
Zheng, Sister.

00:05:52.190 --> 00:05:52.750 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:55.150 line:80%
The fireworks are too loud. I can't sleep.

00:06:18.630 --> 00:06:20.430 line:80%
Changning, take off your shoes.

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:22.040 line:80%
Okay.

00:06:37.670 --> 00:06:39.959 line:80%
I'm helping Sister take off her jacket.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:44.959 line:80%
No need.

00:06:45.990 --> 00:06:47.480 line:80%
If you take off her jacket now,

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:48.610 line:80%
she'll catch a cold.

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:50.870 line:80%
It's alright.

00:06:51.630 --> 00:06:53.600 line:80%
Just let your sister sleep like this.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:54.709 line:80%
Go get the quilt.

00:07:18.650 --> 00:07:19.380 line:80%
Changning.

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:24.940 line:80%
Don't tell your sister

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:26.930 line:80%
what happened tonight.

00:07:26.990 --> 00:07:28.090 line:80%
What happened?

00:07:31.910 --> 00:07:32.740 line:80%
Nothing.

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:06.360 line:80%
[You'll be rich]

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:05.890 line:80%
Zheng.

00:08:07.780 --> 00:08:08.580 line:80%
Zheng.

00:08:16.400 --> 00:08:17.400 line:80%
-Zheng.
-Mother.

00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:21.430 line:80%
It's the first day of the New Year.

00:08:21.430 --> 00:08:22.520 line:80%
Zheng is such a good boy.

00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:23.870 line:80%
You didn't sleep in.

00:08:24.630 --> 00:08:26.310 line:80%
Look carefully around the room.

00:08:26.310 --> 00:08:29.310 line:80%
I prepared a New Year's surprise for you.

00:08:33.920 --> 00:08:35.240 line:80%
Thank you, Mother.

00:08:39.310 --> 00:08:40.400 line:80%
Are you happy?

00:08:40.709 --> 00:08:41.550 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.950 line:80%
Then I will tell you some good news.

00:08:45.010 --> 00:08:46.000 line:80%
Father and Uncle

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.860 line:80%
will be back from the border soon.

00:09:01.550 --> 00:09:01.820 line:80%
[You'll be rich]

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:56.590 line:80%
What's going on?

00:09:57.710 --> 00:09:59.000 line:80%
Last night...

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:23.070 line:80%
Morning.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:23.950 line:80%
Morning.

00:10:37.700 --> 00:10:38.850 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:40.780 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:10:45.470 --> 00:10:46.600 line:80%
Is something wrong?

00:10:48.460 --> 00:10:49.780 line:80%
I just wanted to ask...

00:10:51.830 --> 00:10:53.800 line:80%
Last night...

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:59.550 line:80%
L-Last night?

00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:04.160 line:80%
Do you remember...

00:11:04.310 --> 00:11:05.310 line:80%
I just wanted to say...

00:11:05.310 --> 00:11:06.950 line:80%
Changyu! Changyu!

00:11:07.350 --> 00:11:09.480 line:80%
We're here to wish you a Happy New Year!

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:11.520 line:80%
Manager Yu.

00:11:11.520 --> 00:11:12.470 line:80%
Uncle, Auntie.

00:11:12.470 --> 00:11:14.120 line:80%
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.670 line:80%
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

00:11:15.670 --> 00:11:16.520 line:80%
Happy New Year!

00:11:16.520 --> 00:11:17.800 line:80%
You were just trying to tell me

00:11:17.800 --> 00:11:19.530 line:80%
that they were coming to visit?

00:11:27.880 --> 00:11:29.810 line:80%
Changyu, look who's here!

00:11:30.400 --> 00:11:31.190 line:80%
Qianqian!

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:34.160 line:80%
I didn't expect your place

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:35.400 line:80%
to be so festive.

00:11:35.400 --> 00:11:36.470 line:80%
It's really lively.

00:11:36.470 --> 00:11:37.400 line:80%
Isn't it?

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:40.000 line:80%
Auntie Changyu, Uncle Yanshi, Happy New Year.

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:43.100 line:80%
Happy New Year.
Your hat looks really nice.

00:11:43.950 --> 00:11:45.280 line:80%
Alright, don't just stand there.

00:11:45.280 --> 00:11:46.590 line:80%
-Go inside.
-Yes.

00:11:46.590 --> 00:11:48.240 line:80%
Please, come in.

00:11:48.760 --> 00:11:49.310 line:80%
Let's go.

00:11:50.470 --> 00:11:51.390 line:80%
Come this way.

00:11:58.120 --> 00:11:58.710 line:80%
We would be

00:11:58.710 --> 00:12:00.880 line:80%
-happy with just your presence.
-What is this?

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.040 line:80%
Why did you bring such expensive gifts?

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:05.170 line:80%
You and your husband helped me so much.

00:12:05.190 --> 00:12:05.780 line:80%
I really don't know

00:12:05.780 --> 00:12:07.310 line:80%
how to thank you properly.

00:12:09.470 --> 00:12:12.710 line:80%
That rice merchant surnamed Qi
didn't show up again, did he?

00:12:12.710 --> 00:12:13.800 line:80%
The moment you stepped in,

00:12:13.800 --> 00:12:15.460 line:80%
you're already two men worth.

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:19.790 line:80%
I've been looking forward to you
coming to play with me every day,

00:12:19.790 --> 00:12:21.240 line:80%
but you never came.

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.760 line:80%
It's been too busy at home these days.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:26.120 line:80%
I had to help Sister prepare for
the New Year.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.640 line:80%
How does your family celebrate New Year?

00:12:27.640 --> 00:12:30.060 line:80%
We watched fireworks,

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:31.430 line:80%
ate spicy hot pot,

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:33.670 line:80%
wrote couplets,

00:12:33.970 --> 00:12:35.900 line:80%
built snowmen, and went sledding.

00:12:37.070 --> 00:12:38.290 line:80%
You ate candy?

00:12:41.190 --> 00:12:42.990 line:80%
I hid two pieces.

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.120 line:80%
Here's one for you.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:45.120 line:80%
I didn't dare take more.

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.380 line:80%
I'm worried you'd get cavities.

00:12:46.380 --> 00:12:47.660 line:80%
Thank you, Changning.

00:12:49.880 --> 00:12:50.760 line:80%
Eat slowly.

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:52.470 line:80%
Manager Yu,

00:12:52.830 --> 00:12:54.950 line:80%
stay and have a simple meal with us today.

00:12:54.950 --> 00:12:56.410 line:80%
We made mutton dumplings.

00:12:56.830 --> 00:12:57.710 line:80%
Although it can't compare to

00:12:57.710 --> 00:12:59.640 line:80%
the exquisite food at Yixiang Restaurant,

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:00.920 line:80%
it's better because we're together.

00:13:00.920 --> 00:13:01.830 line:80%
Yes, indeed.

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:02.950 line:80%
Thank you, Auntie.

00:13:02.950 --> 00:13:04.670 line:80%
It's been a long time since
I had mutton dumplings.

00:13:04.670 --> 00:13:05.550 line:80%
Let me help too.

00:13:05.670 --> 00:13:06.310 line:80%
No need.

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:09.930 line:80%
-You and Changyu are not allowed
to enter the kitchen today.
-That's right.

00:13:09.930 --> 00:13:12.530 line:80%
What do you mean 'that's right'?
You come help.

00:13:12.900 --> 00:13:13.570 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:13:13.950 --> 00:13:14.520 line:80%
Let's go.

00:13:16.420 --> 00:13:17.810 line:80%
Look at this.

00:13:18.990 --> 00:13:20.710 line:80%
You could handle this by yourself, right?

00:13:20.710 --> 00:13:21.520 line:80%
No, I need your help.

00:13:21.520 --> 00:13:23.520 line:80%
Do you want to have a snowball fight?

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:25.830 line:80%
But I have to ask my mom.

00:13:26.040 --> 00:13:27.160 line:80%
I heard that.

00:13:27.820 --> 00:13:28.700 line:80%
Fuling.

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:30.310 line:80%
Take them to play. Just don't go too far.

00:13:30.310 --> 00:13:30.830 line:80%
Okay.

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.200 line:80%
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:40.260 line:80%
Bao'er, look. My snowman has arms.

00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:44.760 line:80%
You dare hit me?

00:13:46.280 --> 00:13:48.280 line:80%
Watch out for my super big snowball!

00:13:51.310 --> 00:13:52.350 line:80%
Yu Bao'er!

00:13:56.070 --> 00:13:56.900 line:80%
You dare hit me?

00:13:56.900 --> 00:13:58.760 line:80%
-Take this!
-Look at my snowball.

00:14:04.710 --> 00:14:06.920 line:80%
What an adorable child.

00:14:08.310 --> 00:14:08.830 line:80%
Come.

00:14:09.760 --> 00:14:12.000 line:80%
Take this. Happy New Year.

00:14:13.920 --> 00:14:15.040 line:80%
Take it.

00:14:15.550 --> 00:14:17.160 line:80%
I am getting old,

00:14:17.710 --> 00:14:20.510 line:80%
and I want to get some blessings
from you children.

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:21.900 line:80%
Here you go.

00:14:22.470 --> 00:14:23.220 line:80%
Thank you.

00:14:23.310 --> 00:14:24.240 line:80%
You're welcome.

00:14:24.350 --> 00:14:25.350 line:80%
Thank you, Granny.

00:14:25.350 --> 00:14:26.680 line:80%
Happy New Year, Granny.

00:14:27.070 --> 00:14:28.350 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:14:28.950 --> 00:14:30.310 line:80%
What is your name?

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:32.000 line:80%
How old are you?

00:14:34.350 --> 00:14:35.410 line:80%
My name is Cong'er.

00:14:35.830 --> 00:14:36.960 line:80%
I’m seven years old.

00:14:38.280 --> 00:14:40.540 line:80%
You're about the same age as my grandson.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:42.400 line:80%
He was born in the eighth lunar month.

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:44.030 line:80%
Which month were you born in?

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:46.250 line:80%
The fifth day of the fifth lunar month.

00:14:47.830 --> 00:14:52.140 line:80%
It's the Dragon Boat Festival.
That is a good day.

00:14:58.120 --> 00:14:58.830 line:80%
Changning!

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:03.040 line:80%
Changning!

00:15:03.130 --> 00:15:03.920 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:07.210 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:09.090 --> 00:15:09.870 line:80%
Changning!

00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:15.190 line:80%
Changning!

00:15:16.280 --> 00:15:16.970 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:17.800 --> 00:15:18.600 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:21.350 --> 00:15:22.190 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:24.800 line:80%
-Yu Bao'er!
-Changning!

00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:26.640 line:80%
Yu Bao'er!

00:15:26.830 --> 00:15:27.470 line:80%
Changning!

00:15:27.470 --> 00:15:28.430 line:80%
It's all my fault.

00:15:28.430 --> 00:15:30.190 line:80%
We were building snowmen
at the village entrance.

00:15:30.190 --> 00:15:31.190 line:80%
But I got distracted,

00:15:31.190 --> 00:15:33.470 line:80%
and in the blink of an eye,
Changning and Bao'er were gone.

00:15:33.470 --> 00:15:34.400 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:34.400 --> 00:15:35.160 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:15:35.160 --> 00:15:36.210 line:80%
We will find them.

00:15:36.590 --> 00:15:37.710 line:80%
Yu Bao'er!

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:39.280 line:80%
-Changning!
-Yu Bao'er!

00:15:52.170 --> 00:15:53.840 line:80%
I finally hit you!

00:15:54.190 --> 00:15:55.120 line:80%
Where did you go?

00:15:55.430 --> 00:15:57.310 line:80%
Changning and I went for a snowball fight.

00:15:57.310 --> 00:15:58.710 line:80%
The snow is thicker here.

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:00.310 line:80%
Why didn't you answer when I called you?

00:16:00.310 --> 00:16:01.830 line:80%
I couldn't find you anywhere
along the way.

00:16:01.830 --> 00:16:03.690 line:80%
Do you know you scared me to death?

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:05.550 line:80%
It's okay. We found them now.

00:16:05.550 --> 00:16:06.810 line:80%
Kids just love to play.

00:16:08.280 --> 00:16:09.280 line:80%
It's alright now.

00:16:13.850 --> 00:16:14.850 line:80%
You hit me!

00:16:19.500 --> 00:16:20.470 line:80%
Take this!

00:16:20.700 --> 00:16:21.640 line:80%
Yu Bao'er!

00:16:22.640 --> 00:16:23.790 line:80%
You are done for!

00:16:23.880 --> 00:16:24.640 line:80%
Yu Bao'er!

00:17:05.070 --> 00:17:06.310 line:80%
Whoa.

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:21.280 line:80%
Master,

00:17:21.680 --> 00:17:24.680 line:80%
that child does look a bit like you
when you were young,

00:17:24.700 --> 00:17:26.560 line:80%
but the birth date doesn't match.

00:17:27.830 --> 00:17:28.590 line:80%
Is that so?

00:17:47.290 --> 00:17:48.090 line:80%
Speak.

00:17:48.680 --> 00:17:50.550 line:80%
When is your Little Young Master's

00:17:50.550 --> 00:17:51.720 line:80%
birthday?

00:17:53.630 --> 00:17:54.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:17:54.680 --> 00:17:56.180 line:80%
It was the year of the ox,

00:17:56.590 --> 00:17:58.000 line:80%
on the ninth day of August.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:59.470 line:80%
His name is Bao'er.

00:18:01.830 --> 00:18:02.830 line:80%
Did you hear that?

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:05.490 line:80%
He likes to lie,

00:18:05.880 --> 00:18:07.360 line:80%
just like his mother.

00:18:07.930 --> 00:18:08.880 line:80%
Don't kill me!

00:18:08.900 --> 00:18:09.970 line:80%
Don't kill me!

00:18:15.060 --> 00:18:16.190 line:80%
All of this silver

00:18:16.350 --> 00:18:18.070 line:80%
should last you for the rest of your life.

00:18:18.070 --> 00:18:20.180 line:80%
Leave Lin'an and never come back.

00:18:20.350 --> 00:18:21.750 line:80%
Thank you, Young Master.

00:18:21.800 --> 00:18:23.200 line:80%
Thank you, Young Master.

00:18:24.520 --> 00:18:27.250 line:80%
I will bring Little Young Master home
right away.

00:18:33.050 --> 00:18:36.510 line:80%
Nanny Lan, you are getting more
and more assertive these days.

00:18:49.250 --> 00:18:51.380 line:80%
I was wrong. Please forgive me.

00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:02.610 line:80%
You have taken care of me for years.

00:19:03.630 --> 00:19:05.150 line:80%
You only worry about me.

00:19:07.070 --> 00:19:08.600 line:80%
What crime is there in that?

00:19:11.040 --> 00:19:12.170 line:80%
Don't worry, Nanny.

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:15.560 line:80%
My child will be found sooner or later.

00:19:16.350 --> 00:19:19.630 line:80%
It's just that we still have dealings
with the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:19:19.630 --> 00:19:22.490 line:80%
and I don't want to
destabilize that relationship.

00:19:23.630 --> 00:19:24.440 line:80%
Rest assured,

00:19:25.280 --> 00:19:27.080 line:80%
they cannot escape Lin'an Town.

00:19:28.770 --> 00:19:30.700 line:80%
You are wise, Eldest Young Master.

00:19:30.720 --> 00:19:32.520 line:80%
I was too impatient.

00:19:57.830 --> 00:19:59.840 line:80%
Beating people in broad daylight!

00:20:04.830 --> 00:20:06.630 line:80%
Commissioner Wei has ordered
for grain to be collected.

00:20:06.630 --> 00:20:07.920 line:80%
How dare you resist?

00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:08.760 line:80%
Stop!

00:20:09.070 --> 00:20:10.070 line:80%
Spare us, my lord!

00:20:11.630 --> 00:20:13.030 line:80%
This is Jizhou!

00:20:13.240 --> 00:20:14.760 line:80%
General He has ordered

00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:18.240 line:80%
that soldiers are strictly forbidden from
seizing grain from the people.

00:20:18.240 --> 00:20:18.970 line:80%
Arrest them!

00:20:19.310 --> 00:20:20.110 line:80%
I dare you!

00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:28.380 line:80%
Take them away!

00:20:32.390 --> 00:20:33.680 line:80%
We are Lord Wei's soldiers!

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:34.940 line:80%
How dare you arrest us?

00:20:36.480 --> 00:20:41.070 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:39.830 line:80%
Should we attack the left or the right?

00:20:40.550 --> 00:20:43.110 line:80%
Divide the troops into three groups
to surround them,

00:20:43.110 --> 00:20:44.830 line:80%
-then cut off their grain.
-He Jingyuan!

00:20:44.830 --> 00:20:46.160 line:80%
Get the hell out here!

00:20:49.910 --> 00:20:51.110 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:20:51.280 --> 00:20:53.830 line:80%
what's up? Why all the hurry?

00:20:54.050 --> 00:20:55.890 line:80%
You have some nerve

00:20:56.440 --> 00:20:57.910 line:80%
arresting my men.

00:20:58.630 --> 00:21:00.830 line:80%
Please calm down, Eldest Young Master.

00:21:02.390 --> 00:21:03.590 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:21:04.390 --> 00:21:06.280 line:80%
those soldiers were on the streets

00:21:06.280 --> 00:21:08.440 line:80%
forcibly seizing grain from the people.

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:09.830 line:80%
It caused public outrage,

00:21:09.830 --> 00:21:12.490 line:80%
so I had to detain them at
the government office.

00:21:13.310 --> 00:21:15.910 line:80%
The recent events have been a bit peculiar.

00:21:15.930 --> 00:21:16.800 line:80%
I'm thinking

00:21:16.800 --> 00:21:20.080 line:80%
it must be a trap set by Lord Changxin

00:21:20.110 --> 00:21:22.150 line:80%
and those rebels.

00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:23.680 line:80%
So,

00:21:24.070 --> 00:21:26.000 line:80%
I advise you, Eldest Young Master,

00:21:26.150 --> 00:21:29.000 line:80%
to be careful and not fall for their ruse.

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.040 line:80%
What ruse?

00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:32.390 line:80%
Just because I lost a few battles,

00:21:32.390 --> 00:21:34.550 line:80%
you assume I can't take Chongzhou?

00:21:36.550 --> 00:21:38.390 line:80%
You arrested my men and withheld my grain.

00:21:38.390 --> 00:21:40.330 line:80%
You have no respect for me.

00:21:40.440 --> 00:21:42.150 line:80%
-Eldest Young Master.
-Deliberately shaking the army’s morale.

00:21:42.150 --> 00:21:43.550 line:80%
is an act of aiding the enemy.

00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:44.270 line:80%
Guards!

00:21:44.350 --> 00:21:45.040 line:80%
Here!

00:21:45.310 --> 00:21:48.190 line:80%
Throw He Jingyuan in jail to await trial!

00:21:48.350 --> 00:21:49.070 line:80%
I dare you!

00:21:49.070 --> 00:21:49.630 line:80%
Wait!

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:52.680 line:80%
What are you up to?

00:21:52.910 --> 00:21:54.910 line:80%
Are we fighting amongst ourselves?

00:21:55.070 --> 00:21:57.800 line:80%
Isn't that playing right into
the rebels' hands?

00:22:03.680 --> 00:22:04.880 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:22:06.070 --> 00:22:08.760 line:80%
let me give you one last piece of advice.

00:22:09.590 --> 00:22:10.590 line:80%
Be cautious.

00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:22.390 line:80%
Take him away.

00:22:22.390 --> 00:22:23.050 line:80%
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:22:28.390 --> 00:22:29.110 line:80%
-General!
-General!

00:22:29.110 --> 00:22:29.720 line:80%
-General!
-General.

00:22:29.540 --> 00:22:32.230 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:31.680 line:80%
-General!
-General!

00:22:32.630 --> 00:22:34.260 line:80%
[Order]

00:22:37.500 --> 00:22:45.160 line:80%
[Order]

00:22:40.040 --> 00:22:42.900 line:80%
Here is the order from
the Northwest Commissioner.

00:22:42.910 --> 00:22:45.760 line:80%
I order you to collect grain
in Jizhou immediately.

00:22:45.760 --> 00:22:47.390 line:80%
In three days, by noontime,

00:22:47.670 --> 00:22:53.180 line:80%
[Order]

00:22:47.910 --> 00:22:50.200 line:80%
if I don't see 100,000 picul of grain,

00:22:51.200 --> 00:22:52.590 line:80%
bring me your heads.

00:22:58.310 --> 00:23:00.110 line:80%
100,000 picul of grain?

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:02.410 line:80%
It's impossible to get enough.

00:23:02.550 --> 00:23:03.830 line:80%
General He was taken away,

00:23:03.830 --> 00:23:05.830 line:80%
and we were threatened with swords.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:07.870 line:80%
Captain Li happens to be absent.

00:23:08.110 --> 00:23:09.440 line:80%
What should we do?

00:23:11.850 --> 00:23:15.260 line:80%
[Lantern Festival]

00:23:26.280 --> 00:23:30.080 line:80%
It's been ages since I last came to
the Lantern Festival. How lively!

00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:39.590 line:80%
Lanterns!

00:23:39.590 --> 00:23:41.390 line:80%
Look, this one moves. Look!

00:23:41.760 --> 00:23:42.800 line:80%
Come and see!

00:23:43.630 --> 00:23:46.280 line:80%
-Let’s go.
-Let's not go back to Xigu Lane tonight.

00:23:46.280 --> 00:23:47.000 line:80%
Why?

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:49.830 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant has a banquet tomorrow,

00:23:49.830 --> 00:23:51.760 line:80%
and they need a lot of braised meat.

00:23:51.910 --> 00:23:54.510 line:80%
Qianqian asked me to go help
tomorrow morning.

00:23:56.590 --> 00:23:57.790 line:80%
Come. I'll carry you.

00:23:58.850 --> 00:23:59.540 line:80%
Be careful.

00:24:21.900 --> 00:24:23.920 line:80%
Then let's find an inn to stay.

00:24:24.630 --> 00:24:26.150 line:80%
Qianqian said she had already
made arrangements.

00:24:26.150 --> 00:24:27.750 line:80%
We can just stay at her place.

00:24:31.390 --> 00:24:32.350 line:80%
Fireworks!

00:24:34.470 --> 00:24:35.650 line:80%
Let me carry her.

00:24:36.580 --> 00:24:38.550 line:80%
Your hand injury hasn't healed yet.

00:24:38.550 --> 00:24:40.010 line:80%
Carrying a child won't hurt.

00:24:40.010 --> 00:24:41.150 line:80%
On this street, it seems like

00:24:41.150 --> 00:24:44.410 line:80%
all the children are carried by
their fathers or brothers.

00:24:49.040 --> 00:24:50.630 line:80%
Tell me when you get tired.

00:24:50.630 --> 00:24:51.150 line:80%
Okay.

00:24:51.830 --> 00:24:52.550 line:80%
Which way?

00:24:52.550 --> 00:24:53.590 line:80%
That way.

00:24:54.350 --> 00:24:55.240 line:80%
Over there.

00:24:58.600 --> 00:25:01.000 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:25:01.780 --> 00:25:03.370 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:25:04.190 --> 00:25:06.730 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:25:07.360 --> 00:25:09.870 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:25:10.540 --> 00:25:12.200 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:25:12.780 --> 00:25:17.490 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:25:20.100 --> 00:25:21.260 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:25:21.290 --> 00:25:23.860 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:25:24.530 --> 00:25:25.400 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:25:25.430 --> 00:25:27.810 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:25:28.550 --> 00:25:32.460 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:25:33.010 --> 00:25:36.530 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:25:37.500 --> 00:25:38.280 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:25:38.300 --> 00:25:40.900 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:25:42.130 --> 00:25:42.960 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:25:42.990 --> 00:25:45.550 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:25:46.140 --> 00:25:50.180 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:25:48.440 --> 00:25:49.890 line:80%
Come and take a look!

00:25:48.910 --> 00:25:53.190 line:80%
[Dumplings]

00:25:50.040 --> 00:25:52.430 line:80%
Lantern wishes made during
the Lantern Festival are the most efficacious.

00:25:50.620 --> 00:25:58.880 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:25:52.480 --> 00:25:54.760 line:80%
If you miss it, you'll have to
wait another year!

00:25:54.760 --> 00:25:56.520 line:80%
Would you two like to buy one?

00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:12.070 line:80%
Do you want one?

00:26:12.250 --> 00:26:13.150 line:80%
No need.

00:26:13.480 --> 00:26:14.070 line:80%
Let's go.

00:26:36.310 --> 00:26:37.110 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:26:47.480 --> 00:26:50.340 line:80%
Look. They all have Song Yan's name
written on them.

00:26:50.910 --> 00:26:52.240 line:80%
He's no good man.

00:26:53.350 --> 00:26:55.810 line:80%
Since when did these ladies
become so blind?

00:26:56.310 --> 00:26:59.800 line:80%
Making a wish to be with him
is just setting a trap for yourself, no?

00:26:59.800 --> 00:27:00.600 line:80%
This can't be.

00:27:01.550 --> 00:27:02.610 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:27:03.040 --> 00:27:03.970 line:80%
I'm saving them.

00:27:04.270 --> 00:27:07.680 line:80%
[Song Yan]

00:27:07.590 --> 00:27:09.150 line:80%
If you wipe them off like this,

00:27:09.150 --> 00:27:10.480 line:80%
you'll get beaten if they see you.

00:27:10.480 --> 00:27:11.910 line:80%
I'm saving them.

00:27:12.760 --> 00:27:14.040 line:80%
What's that saying?

00:27:17.200 --> 00:27:18.930 line:80%
If the cart in front overturns,

00:27:19.200 --> 00:27:22.000 line:80%
we mustn't let carts behind
fall into the same pit.

00:27:26.590 --> 00:27:28.350 line:80%
There are so many lanterns in the river.

00:27:28.350 --> 00:27:30.610 line:80%
How long will it take you to wipe them all?

00:27:31.590 --> 00:27:33.790 line:80%
Why are there so many ladies this blind?

00:27:39.910 --> 00:27:40.760 line:80%
It seems...

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:44.100 line:80%
you also released lanterns for Song Yan
in the past.

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:47.240 line:80%
All the money I saved up
went toward his tuition fees.

00:27:47.300 --> 00:27:48.680 line:80%
I had no money for these.

00:27:50.440 --> 00:27:53.100 line:80%
Changning wants that piggy lantern
over there.

00:27:54.200 --> 00:27:54.830 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:27:57.550 --> 00:27:58.390 line:80%
Be careful.

00:28:01.280 --> 00:28:01.830 line:80%
Let's go.

00:28:09.870 --> 00:28:11.200 line:80%
Song Yan.

00:28:38.450 --> 00:28:41.320 line:80%
[Lantern]

00:28:38.870 --> 00:28:39.940 line:80%
Pick one.

00:28:40.350 --> 00:28:41.480 line:80%
I want this one.

00:28:46.310 --> 00:28:47.440 line:80%
Changyu?

00:28:47.830 --> 00:28:48.480 line:80%
Changyu!

00:28:59.390 --> 00:29:00.000 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:00.440 --> 00:29:01.870 line:80%
A good dog doesn't get in the way.

00:29:01.870 --> 00:29:02.480 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:03.680 --> 00:29:04.350 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:29:06.390 --> 00:29:09.070 line:80%
Have you always regretted
having no chance to release a lantern?

00:29:09.070 --> 00:29:10.270 line:80%
I'll make it up to you.

00:29:10.520 --> 00:29:12.070 line:80%
Shall we write both our names on it?

00:29:12.070 --> 00:29:13.550 line:80%
You are disgusting.

00:29:14.310 --> 00:29:16.570 line:80%
I'm speaking from the bottom of my heart.

00:29:16.910 --> 00:29:18.570 line:80%
From the bottom of your heart?

00:29:24.590 --> 00:29:26.720 line:80%
Everyone, come and look!

00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:29.580 line:80%
Scholar Song gave me a lantern.

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:30.870 line:80%
He said he wanted to sincerely

00:29:30.870 --> 00:29:31.780 line:80%
-apologize to me!
-Stop it!

00:29:31.780 --> 00:29:32.840 line:80%
He even gave me a lantern!

00:29:32.840 --> 00:29:34.040 line:80%
-Everyone!
-Shut up!

00:29:35.150 --> 00:29:36.100 line:80%
What is it?

00:29:36.390 --> 00:29:39.190 line:80%
You dare say it,
but you won't let everyone hear it?

00:29:39.690 --> 00:29:41.830 line:80%
Clearly, you're the one
still obsessed with me.

00:29:41.830 --> 00:29:43.980 line:80%
I only played along out of pity
for your feelings.

00:29:43.980 --> 00:29:45.550 line:80%
-You...
-Song Yan!

00:29:52.310 --> 00:29:54.910 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:29:55.480 --> 00:29:56.420 line:80%
Qianjin.

00:29:57.310 --> 00:29:58.150 line:80%
Qianjin.

00:29:59.910 --> 00:30:01.370 line:80%
I came to buy you a lantern,

00:30:01.910 --> 00:30:05.040 line:80%
but I saw Changyu with
her lingering affection for me.

00:30:05.440 --> 00:30:06.500 line:80%
She was jealous and

00:30:06.760 --> 00:30:08.590 line:80%
was ruining other ladies' lanterns.

00:30:08.590 --> 00:30:09.550 line:80%
That's why I stepped in to stop her.

00:30:09.550 --> 00:30:10.520 line:80%
Nonsense!

00:30:11.830 --> 00:30:13.280 line:80%
I was trying to pull these young ladies

00:30:13.280 --> 00:30:14.830 line:80%
out of the mud pit.

00:30:15.280 --> 00:30:16.220 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:30:17.040 --> 00:30:19.520 line:80%
You really have deep feelings

00:30:19.830 --> 00:30:21.310 line:80%
for my dearest Song Yan.

00:30:23.280 --> 00:30:24.580 line:80%
You knew he would

00:30:24.610 --> 00:30:25.870 line:80%
come to the lantern fair tonight.

00:30:25.870 --> 00:30:27.470 line:80%
So you eagerly ran over here,

00:30:27.550 --> 00:30:28.960 line:80%
just to see him once.

00:30:30.340 --> 00:30:32.070 line:80%
She's always been obsessed with me,

00:30:32.070 --> 00:30:34.150 line:80%
and has been destroying
other people's lanterns here.

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:34.800 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:30:37.000 --> 00:30:38.910 line:80%
You are already a married woman,

00:30:38.910 --> 00:30:41.210 line:80%
yet all you do is harass Song Yan.

00:30:41.440 --> 00:30:43.290 line:80%
What a nuisance you are.

00:30:41.870 --> 00:30:45.550 line:80%
[Lantern]

00:30:43.390 --> 00:30:46.040 line:80%
I've never seen someone so shameless.

00:30:47.760 --> 00:30:49.110 line:80%
Our relationship has run its course.

00:30:49.110 --> 00:30:50.200 line:80%
Stop pestering me.

00:30:51.240 --> 00:30:51.990 line:80%
Qianjin,

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:53.630 line:80%
let's go to the other side.

00:30:53.630 --> 00:30:54.240 line:80%
I don't want to.

00:30:54.240 --> 00:30:55.130 line:80%
Miss Cui.

00:30:55.480 --> 00:30:57.030 line:80%
I don't mind giving you

00:30:57.200 --> 00:30:58.200 line:80%
a piece of trash like Song Yan.

00:30:58.200 --> 00:31:00.150 line:80%
But let me give you a piece of advice.

00:31:00.150 --> 00:31:01.110 line:80%
This man

00:31:01.910 --> 00:31:03.920 line:80%
loves two-timing the most.

00:31:04.200 --> 00:31:05.830 line:80%
Don't let him fool you.

00:31:07.310 --> 00:31:08.590 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:31:09.720 --> 00:31:13.400 line:80%
You failed to be
a scholar's wife as a butcher,

00:31:13.550 --> 00:31:15.550 line:80%
so you are spouting nonsense here.

00:31:19.800 --> 00:31:20.860 line:80%
This guy right here

00:31:21.390 --> 00:31:23.680 line:80%
is bound to rub shoulders with
even nobler figures

00:31:23.680 --> 00:31:25.680 line:80%
and climb even higher in the future.

00:31:25.800 --> 00:31:27.040 line:80%
You and the Magistrate

00:31:27.040 --> 00:31:29.700 line:80%
are just stepping stones
for him and his mother.

00:31:30.280 --> 00:31:30.940 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:31:31.310 --> 00:31:33.640 line:80%
why hasn't he proposed to your family yet?

00:31:36.700 --> 00:31:38.300 line:80%
Y-You're talking nonsense.

00:31:41.440 --> 00:31:42.690 line:80%
Qianjin,

00:31:43.390 --> 00:31:45.050 line:80%
I am truly sincere toward you.

00:31:49.520 --> 00:31:50.350 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:31:50.680 --> 00:31:51.520 line:80%
I know.

00:31:52.190 --> 00:31:53.770 line:80%
You want to use such remarks

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:56.830 line:80%
to drive a wedge between me
and Song Yan.

00:31:56.830 --> 00:31:58.200 line:80%
My dearest Song Yan

00:31:58.390 --> 00:32:00.070 line:80%
just wanted to prioritize his studies.

00:32:00.070 --> 00:32:01.470 line:80%
Prioritize his studies?

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:05.960 line:80%
When you made a promise to
the Fan family ten years ago,

00:32:05.960 --> 00:32:07.630 line:80%
your excuse was also to
prioritize your studies.

00:32:07.630 --> 00:32:09.830 line:80%
Why is it still the same excuse
ten years later?

00:32:09.830 --> 00:32:11.230 line:80%
-Don't you dare!
-You...

00:32:12.390 --> 00:32:13.040 line:80%
Fine.

00:32:14.550 --> 00:32:15.830 line:80%
Let's wait and see.

00:32:18.590 --> 00:32:19.680 line:80%
-Qianjin!
-Stop!

00:32:27.150 --> 00:32:27.960 line:80%
You there.

00:32:28.630 --> 00:32:29.290 line:80%
Apologize.

00:32:29.440 --> 00:32:31.100 line:80%
Why should I apologize to her?

00:32:31.240 --> 00:32:33.700 line:80%
For flirting with
a married woman in public.

00:32:33.910 --> 00:32:36.500 line:80%
And when you failed, you resort to slander.

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:39.100 line:80%
Is this how a scholar behaves?

00:32:40.070 --> 00:32:42.110 line:80%
Have you forgotten
the manners of a gentleman?

00:32:42.110 --> 00:32:44.370 line:80%
You sure are good at wagging your tongue.

00:32:45.070 --> 00:32:45.680 line:80%
What?

00:32:46.870 --> 00:32:48.670 line:80%
Are you from Fengxiao Pavilion?

00:32:49.280 --> 00:32:50.210 line:80%
What did you say?

00:32:50.680 --> 00:32:51.240 line:80%
You!

00:32:53.440 --> 00:32:54.960 line:80%
Laughing? What are you laughing at?

00:32:54.960 --> 00:32:55.550 line:80%
You...

00:32:56.390 --> 00:32:57.680 line:80%
You are a disgrace to scholars!

00:32:57.680 --> 00:32:59.880 line:80%
"Scholar"? Are you worthy of that word?

00:33:00.240 --> 00:33:01.390 line:80%
You might have studied for a bit,

00:33:01.390 --> 00:33:03.280 line:80%
and now you look down on everyone.

00:33:03.550 --> 00:33:04.480 line:80%
How do you know

00:33:05.350 --> 00:33:07.350 line:80%
that when the northern geese fly south,

00:33:07.350 --> 00:33:10.010 line:80%
the phoenixes won't be able find
a place to land?

00:33:11.070 --> 00:33:12.680 line:80%
It was clearly Changyu who couldn't

00:33:12.680 --> 00:33:14.280 line:80%
get over me, Song Yan, first.

00:33:15.550 --> 00:33:16.390 line:80%
Song Yan?

00:33:18.390 --> 00:33:19.390 line:80%
Who is Song Yan?

00:33:20.070 --> 00:33:20.760 line:80%
Yeah.

00:33:20.870 --> 00:33:22.280 line:80%
My sister has long forgotten you,

00:33:22.280 --> 00:33:23.830 line:80%
you big bad villain. Pfft!

00:33:26.240 --> 00:33:27.270 line:80%
This kid...

00:33:30.870 --> 00:33:33.440 line:80%
-Leaving?
-Why are you leaving?

00:33:36.110 --> 00:33:36.970 line:80%
Still unhappy?

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:39.970 line:80%
I don't know why,

00:33:40.440 --> 00:33:42.300 line:80%
but I still don't feel satisfied.

00:33:45.310 --> 00:33:46.630 line:80%
I came out to visit the lantern market,

00:33:46.630 --> 00:33:47.870 line:80%
but ran into Fan Changyu instead.

00:33:47.870 --> 00:33:48.830 line:80%
What bad luck!

00:33:50.520 --> 00:33:51.480 line:80%
Qianjin, there is no need

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:53.340 line:80%
to argue with such vulgar people.

00:33:54.240 --> 00:33:55.500 line:80%
Take care of yourself.

00:33:55.760 --> 00:33:56.820 line:80%
I'll go back first.

00:33:56.910 --> 00:33:57.720 line:80%
Qianjin。

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:02.800 line:80%
Take care, Qianjin.

00:34:14.310 --> 00:34:16.200 line:80%
Just a pretty boy who married into
his wife's family.

00:34:16.200 --> 00:34:18.510 line:80%
If he really had the ability to
pass the imperial exam,

00:34:18.510 --> 00:34:21.030 line:80%
he wouldn't be a live-in son-in-law.

00:34:23.390 --> 00:34:24.280 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:34:24.870 --> 00:34:26.600 line:80%
if he really takes the exam,

00:34:27.350 --> 00:34:30.280 line:80%
he probably won't even pass
the preliminary exams.

00:34:32.120 --> 00:34:32.800 line:80%
One.

00:34:33.800 --> 00:34:34.560 line:80%
Two.

00:34:35.870 --> 00:34:36.600 line:80%
Three.

00:34:38.760 --> 00:34:39.570 line:80%
Four.

00:34:40.310 --> 00:34:41.570 line:80%
Why are you hitting me?

00:34:41.680 --> 00:34:42.510 line:80%
Five.

00:34:43.390 --> 00:34:44.390 line:80%
Don't hit my face!

00:34:44.470 --> 00:34:45.370 line:80%
Six.

00:34:45.430 --> 00:34:46.570 line:80%
Go easy on me!

00:34:47.560 --> 00:34:48.390 line:80%
Seven.

00:34:49.840 --> 00:34:51.650 line:80%
I only counted till seven!

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:00.910 line:80%
Wait!

00:35:01.830 --> 00:35:02.600 line:80%
No need to run.

00:35:02.600 --> 00:35:03.600 line:80%
He can't catch up.

00:35:08.530 --> 00:35:09.360 line:80%
Changning.

00:35:25.120 --> 00:35:26.530 line:80%
♪ In troubled times ♪

00:35:26.550 --> 00:35:30.070 line:80%
♪ Who remains amidst the snowstorm? ♪

00:35:31.730 --> 00:35:32.940 line:80%
♪ How many people ♪

00:35:32.960 --> 00:35:36.020 line:80%
♪ Are hanging by a thread? ♪

00:35:35.050 --> 00:35:36.060 line:80%
It's snowing.

00:35:37.160 --> 00:35:39.490 line:80%
♪ As the smoke of war rises over
our homeland ♪

00:35:40.090 --> 00:35:43.210 line:80%
♪ Who can stand apart from the world? ♪

00:35:44.090 --> 00:35:45.700 line:80%
♪ The sunset is gone ♪

00:35:45.720 --> 00:35:47.710 line:80%
♪ And I'm speechless ♪

00:35:49.990 --> 00:35:50.760 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:35:50.540 --> 00:35:51.920 line:80%
♪ As autumn descends ♪

00:35:51.940 --> 00:35:55.710 line:80%
♪ Who treads lightly upon the maple leaves
as they leave? ♪

00:35:53.120 --> 00:35:54.180 line:80%
Your hair is messy.

00:35:55.280 --> 00:35:56.010 line:80%
Turn around.

00:35:56.770 --> 00:35:58.120 line:80%
♪ As light rain falls over wutong trees ♪

00:35:58.140 --> 00:36:01.560 line:80%
♪ Under the eaves,
spring swallows carry mud in their beaks ♪

00:36:01.940 --> 00:36:04.850 line:80%
♪ The bustling atmosphere
of this ancient town ♪

00:36:05.450 --> 00:36:08.120 line:80%
♪ For whom does it unexpectedly unfold? ♪

00:36:09.470 --> 00:36:11.320 line:80%
♪ Let's vow to be together
through life and death ♪

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:14.940 line:80%
♪ And may our vows come true ♪

00:36:17.320 --> 00:36:20.140 line:80%
♪ I'm cautious about destiny ♪

00:36:20.520 --> 00:36:22.810 line:80%
♪ But I won't give up ♪

00:36:23.600 --> 00:36:26.190 line:80%
♪ Alas, the chaos of war and
the clatter of hooves ♪

00:36:26.750 --> 00:36:28.900 line:80%
♪ Ended our story ♪

00:36:29.940 --> 00:36:32.910 line:80%
♪ The comings and goings in
the mortal world are intermittent ♪

00:36:33.460 --> 00:36:37.410 line:80%
♪ You turned away, frowning,
and left with your sword drawn ♪

00:36:37.810 --> 00:36:41.870 line:80%
♪ Taking all the secrets with you ♪

00:36:42.550 --> 00:36:45.410 line:80%
♪ I'm cautious about destiny ♪

00:36:45.710 --> 00:36:48.030 line:80%
♪ But I won't give up ♪

00:36:48.730 --> 00:36:50.530 line:80%
I want my hair tied too.

00:36:49.090 --> 00:36:51.370 line:80%
♪ But we are always on the battlefield ♪

00:36:52.020 --> 00:36:54.510 line:80%
♪ And meeting among the flames of war ♪

00:36:55.220 --> 00:36:58.320 line:80%
♪ Entangled in fate, you gave me ♪

00:36:58.880 --> 00:37:01.270 line:80%
♪ Memories as warm as jade ♪

00:37:01.560 --> 00:37:07.170 line:80%
♪ Having been through countless battles ♪

00:37:07.970 --> 00:37:13.360 line:80%
♪ We finally return to
where we first met ♪

00:37:10.310 --> 00:37:14.750 line:80%
[Tea]

00:37:15.870 --> 00:37:17.120 line:80%
Mr. Sun!

00:37:17.800 --> 00:37:18.600 line:80%
Changning!

00:37:19.430 --> 00:37:20.390 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:37:20.390 --> 00:37:22.120 line:80%
You're getting more adorable.

00:37:24.510 --> 00:37:25.600 line:80%
Mr. Sun.

00:37:26.160 --> 00:37:28.470 line:80%
Greetings, Mrs. Fan and Yan.

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:30.960 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:37:31.160 --> 00:37:34.030 line:80%
I saw your family of three
from the attic just now.

00:37:34.030 --> 00:37:35.230 line:80%
It looked wonderful.

00:37:35.280 --> 00:37:38.660 line:80%
Both of you are truly
a match made in Heaven.

00:37:38.840 --> 00:37:39.790 line:80%
Even the little girl

00:37:39.790 --> 00:37:41.800 line:80%
is so lovable.

00:37:42.790 --> 00:37:44.430 line:80%
So I painted a picture

00:37:44.910 --> 00:37:47.390 line:80%
as a New Year's gift for you.

00:37:47.720 --> 00:37:49.720 line:80%
Wishing your family a harmonious year ahead,

00:37:49.720 --> 00:37:51.920 line:80%
and may you welcome another little son.

00:37:53.830 --> 00:37:55.200 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

00:37:56.080 --> 00:37:57.600 line:80%
Did you come to Lin'an just to paint?

00:37:57.600 --> 00:37:59.720 line:80%
No. I still have business to attend to.

00:37:59.720 --> 00:38:01.770 line:80%
Hence, I need your husband for a bit.

00:38:03.910 --> 00:38:05.600 line:80%
Take Changning to play for a while first.

00:38:05.600 --> 00:38:06.560 line:80%
I'll have a chat

00:38:06.560 --> 00:38:07.310 line:80%
with Mr. Sun.

00:38:08.760 --> 00:38:09.820 line:80%
Have the umbrella.

00:38:09.990 --> 00:38:10.560 line:80%
Let's go.

00:38:11.960 --> 00:38:12.530 line:80%
Let's go.

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:19.810 line:80%
Wei Xuan was recently defeated,

00:38:19.810 --> 00:38:22.470 line:80%
and then imprisoned He Jingyuan
over grain requisition.

00:38:22.470 --> 00:38:24.350 line:80%
Now the soldiers of Jizhou and Yanzhou

00:38:24.350 --> 00:38:27.200 line:80%
all have grievances against
this new Military Commissioner.

00:38:27.200 --> 00:38:28.560 line:80%
Li Huai'an is stranded in the Capital.

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:30.760 line:80%
The Jizhou army is currently leaderless.

00:38:30.760 --> 00:38:32.430 line:80%
The situation is just as you predicted.

00:38:32.430 --> 00:38:34.290 line:80%
That old scoundrel Lord Changxin

00:38:34.470 --> 00:38:35.950 line:80%
will definitely seize this opportunity

00:38:35.950 --> 00:38:36.830 line:80%
to make a move.

00:38:38.280 --> 00:38:40.080 line:80%
The situation is growing critical.

00:38:40.080 --> 00:38:41.610 line:80%
It's time for you to go back.

00:38:45.680 --> 00:38:47.200 line:80%
We've known each other for so long,

00:38:47.200 --> 00:38:49.430 line:80%
yet I still don't know
when your birthday is.

00:38:49.430 --> 00:38:51.230 line:80%
My birthday is easy to remember.

00:38:51.280 --> 00:38:52.800 line:80%
It's 2 days after the Lantern Festival.

00:38:52.800 --> 00:38:54.390 line:80%
The holiday spirit is still strong then.

00:38:54.390 --> 00:38:55.390 line:80%
It's very lively.

00:39:02.330 --> 00:39:03.530 line:80%
We set off

00:39:04.020 --> 00:39:04.820 line:80%
in three days.

00:39:06.950 --> 00:39:08.550 line:80%
Why don't you leave tonight?

00:39:14.590 --> 00:39:15.390 line:80%
Let's go look ahead.

00:39:15.390 --> 00:39:15.990 line:80%
Okay.

00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:17.320 line:80%
What else do you want?

00:39:17.720 --> 00:39:18.430 line:80%
Do you want a rattle drum?

00:39:18.430 --> 00:39:19.120 line:80%
Sure.

00:39:20.870 --> 00:39:22.160 line:80%
Fine, I get it.

00:39:24.310 --> 00:39:27.170 line:80%
How is the investigation into
the Fan family going?

00:39:27.990 --> 00:39:29.470 line:80%
So far, we only found out

00:39:29.470 --> 00:39:32.470 line:80%
that Mrs. Fan's father met
He Jingyuan before he died.

00:39:33.350 --> 00:39:35.610 line:80%
They might have been old acquaintances.

00:39:36.350 --> 00:39:38.410 line:80%
But we found no connection to Wei Yan.

00:39:39.910 --> 00:39:41.080 line:80%
As for Sui Yuanhuai,

00:39:41.080 --> 00:39:43.740 line:80%
he found out that around the time
I was attacked,

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:46.870 line:80%
Wei Yan secretly dealt with
the household guards from that year.

00:39:46.870 --> 00:39:47.560 line:80%
Who?

00:39:48.960 --> 00:39:51.310 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son, Sui Yuanhuai?

00:39:51.310 --> 00:39:52.390 line:80%
You met him here?

00:39:52.950 --> 00:39:54.390 line:80%
What is he doing in Lin'an?

00:39:54.390 --> 00:39:55.250 line:80%
Because of you?

00:39:57.160 --> 00:39:58.390 line:80%
Probably not for me.

00:40:00.470 --> 00:40:02.030 line:80%
But it also doesn't make sense that

00:40:02.030 --> 00:40:03.870 line:80%
he would chase that female shopkeeper

00:40:03.870 --> 00:40:05.330 line:80%
all the way down to Lin'an.

00:40:05.390 --> 00:40:07.120 line:80%
Who is this female shopkeeper?

00:40:07.330 --> 00:40:09.460 line:80%
Wait, I've only been gone half a month.

00:40:09.560 --> 00:40:11.830 line:80%
I can't understand what
you're saying anymore.

00:40:11.830 --> 00:40:13.490 line:80%
Tell me everything in detail.

00:40:21.510 --> 00:40:22.280 line:80%
I see.

00:40:23.470 --> 00:40:25.470 line:80%
You've been quite diligent lately.

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:26.240 line:80%
How come?

00:40:26.680 --> 00:40:28.280 line:80%
You aren't trapped by chess?

00:40:32.080 --> 00:40:33.640 line:80%
Some endgames

00:40:34.800 --> 00:40:36.560 line:80%
cannot be solved in a moment.

00:40:38.130 --> 00:40:39.730 line:80%
I want to set it aside for now.

00:40:43.970 --> 00:40:46.170 line:80%
How did you get Li Huai'an transferred?

00:40:48.730 --> 00:40:50.460 line:80%
I don't have that kind of power.

00:40:50.830 --> 00:40:53.430 line:80%
It was just a coincidence.

00:41:16.830 --> 00:41:17.890 line:80%
Captain Li.

00:41:19.830 --> 00:41:23.690 line:80%
Did you get bored of drinking,
watching plays, and listening to songs

00:41:24.120 --> 00:41:24.990 line:80%
with me today?

00:41:26.080 --> 00:41:27.390 line:80%
It is my honor.

00:41:30.080 --> 00:41:30.870 line:80%
Honor?

00:41:32.470 --> 00:41:33.350 line:80%
I'll be blunt.

00:41:33.870 --> 00:41:35.270 line:80%
I have no interest in you.

00:41:37.430 --> 00:41:39.760 line:80%
Thank you for your candor, Your Highness.

00:41:40.350 --> 00:41:42.680 line:80%
But our marriage is decided by our elders,

00:41:43.760 --> 00:41:45.490 line:80%
and it's not what I want either.

00:41:59.600 --> 00:42:00.510 line:80%
Leave us.

00:42:26.510 --> 00:42:27.720 line:80%
I have a plan that

00:42:28.510 --> 00:42:30.040 line:80%
will bring peace to us both.

00:42:30.310 --> 00:42:31.170 line:80%
What do you say?

00:42:32.250 --> 00:42:34.050 line:80%
I would like to hear the details.

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:46.720 line:80%
Should I go notify them on your behalf?

00:42:46.720 --> 00:42:49.200 line:80%
No need. Do not disturb them.

00:43:01.760 --> 00:43:02.570 line:80%
It is late.

00:43:02.720 --> 00:43:05.060 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, you should get some rest.

00:43:05.560 --> 00:43:06.680 line:80%
Thank you, Fuling.

00:43:16.990 --> 00:43:20.640 line:80%
This must be the surprise Qianqian mentioned.